panels.name: Threats Mitigated
panels.queryString:
_source="SentinelOne"
| parse "eventDesc=*|" as eventDesc
| eventDesc matches "New active threat*" OR eventDesc matches "New Suspicious threat detected*" ? 1 : 0 as active 
| eventDesc="Threat marked as resolved" ? 1 : 0 as resolved
| eventDesc="Quarantine performed successfully" ? 1 : 0 as mitigated
| sum(active) as active, sum(resolved) as resolved, sum(mitigated) as mitigated
| mitigated-resolved as Threats_Mitigated
| fields Threats_Mitigated

panels.name: Total Unresolved Threats
panels.queryString:
_source="SentinelOne"
| parse "eventDesc=*|" as eventDesc
| eventDesc matches "New active threat*" OR eventDesc matches "New Suspicious threat detected*" ? 1 : 0 as active 
| eventDesc="Threat marked as resolved" ? 1 : 0 as resolved
| sum(active) as active, sum(resolved) as resolved
| active-resolved as active_unresolved
| fields active_unresolved

panels.name: New Suspicious file
panels.queryString:
_source="SentinelOne" "Suspicious"
| parse "fileName=*|" as file_name
| parse "sourceHostName=*|" as machine_name
| timeslice 1d
| count by _timeslice, machine_name,file_name
| sort by machine_name asc

panels.name: Most events per PC
panels.queryString:
_source="SentinelOne"
| parse "fileName=*|" as file_name
| parse "eventDesc=New active threat - machine *|" as machine_name
| count_distinct(machine_name) by file_name 
| top 15 file_name by _count_distinct

panels.name: Threats Killed by Machine
panels.queryString:
_source="SentinelOne" "kill"
| parse "threatClassification=*|" as threat_type
| parse "sourceHostName=*|" as machine_name
| timeslice 1d
| count by _timeslice,machine_name,threat_type
| sort by machine_name asc

panels.name: Threats Resolved
panels.queryString:
_source="SentinelOne" "Threat marked as resolved"
| parse "filePath=*|" as file_path
| timeslice 1d
| count by _timeslice, file_path

panels.name: New File Threats
panels.queryString:
_source="SentinelOne" "New active threat"
| parse "filePath=*|" as file_path
| parse "eventDesc=New active threat - machine *|" as machine_name
| parse "fileName=*|" as file_name
| parse "sourceUserName=*|" as user
| count machine_name,file_path,file_name,user

panels.name: New Active Threat by Machine
panels.queryString:
_source="SentinelOne" "New active threat"
| parse "threatClassification=*|" as threat_type
| parse "machine *|" as machine_name
| timeslice 1d
| count by _timeslice,machine_name,threat_type
| sort by machine_name asc

panels.name: By Threat Type
panels.queryString:
_source="SentinelOne"
| parse "threatClassification=*|" as threat_type
| parse "machine *|" as machine_name
| count_distinct(machine_name) by threat_type

panels.name: Threats Quarantined by Machine
panels.queryString:
_source="SentinelOne" "quarantine"
| parse "threatClassification=*|" as threat_type
| parse "sourceHostName=*|" as machine_name
| timeslice 1d
| count by _timeslice,machine_name,threat_type
| sort by machine_name asc

panels.name: Active Threats
panels.queryString:
_source="SentinelOne"
| parse "eventDesc=*|" as eventDesc
| eventDesc matches "New active threat*" OR eventDesc matches "New Suspicious threat detected*" ? 1 : 0 as active 
| eventDesc="Threat marked as resolved" ? 1 : 0 as resolved
| eventDesc="Quarantine performed successfully" ? 1 : 0 as mitigated
| sum(active) as active, sum(resolved) as resolved, sum(mitigated) as mitigated
| active-mitigated as Active_Threats
| fields Active_Threats
